snippet.title: Switch To Dash
snippet.description:
Tap to left or right to switch color and match the path in this impossible challenge! 

Improves your coordination skills and reflexes, pass through lasers,  fly, jump and discover new obstacles along the way.

Challenge yourself in that amazing addictive platformer! 
I warn you: that game it's not so easy! Be prepared for the challenge!

Avaiable on Google Play:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.agamebyme.switchtodash
